{"tid":1738022,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］理工人質事件：我地不停被政府帶緊風向","createTime":"2019-11-19T06:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T05:08:45.000Z","uid":122413,"like":189,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"e9914ec6eb178a42f8709700f96f865dcf6d5688","tid":1738022,"uid":122413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:19:52.000Z","msg":"今朝777出黎講左兩件好重要既訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 「主導權」唔係政府度，係班學生度<br />\n2. 全部示威者必須「投降」<br />\n<br />\n根本原本一開始係班狗圍住都圍出入口<br />\n係想<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">軟禁學生</span></strong><br />\n但政府僵持落去（唔放人，搵曬理大班學生）<br />\n出於人道危機<br />\n國際壓力一定愈來愈大<br />\n而且狗力到達上限 捱唔耐<br />\n而政府都好清楚呢個情況<br />\n<br />\n所以立即琴日晏就開始叫人「投降」「自首」<br />\n令到件事變成班學生有得揀 有選擇<br />\n唔再係軟禁<br />\n但請大家諗清楚咩叫「投降」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<br />\n大家都唔好再用「投降」或者「自首」字眼<br />\n<br />\n成件事根本就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">理工人質事件</span></span><br />\n政府逼軟禁學生來換取交通順暢既籌碼"},{"pid":"f4caf117b1ae1ffd4274ee6dab02090ee565923e","tid":1738022,"uid":122413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:20:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7262c36c36533d3ce28d306a62594be9eb4dcce7","tid":1738022,"uid":122413,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:21:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">提提大家<br />\n現家poly仲有過百位人質係理大入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"dff1a06aa7e9131a2665d25f5ccebe0cbf86defe","tid":1738022,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4443721ee5efad658fbfc318ddff3faffeb92559","tid":1738022,"uid":122413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:22:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d75269fc57dee6a970243b0e4de9096463007df5","tid":1738